| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2022-1099 — Mass File Rename (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 27d9408f-9861-5412-ba0a-545e7bd22849"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
